[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
Before enabling netbird-server:

1. Copy %%PREFIX%%/etc/netbird/netbird-server.yml.sample to
   %%PREFIX%%/etc/netbird/netbird-server.yml.
2. Set server.exposedAddress, server.authSecret, TLS paths, and persistent
   store encryption keys.
3. Enable the service:

   sysrc netbird_server_enable=YES
   service netbird_server start

The sample configuration listens on :8443 and disables local STUN by default
to avoid privileged UDP ports during first validation. Adjust it for the final
deployment topology.
EOM
}
]
